                <h3> Banaras </h3>
                <p> Varanasi grew as an important industrial centre famous for its muslin and silk fabrics, perfumes, ivory works, and sculpture.  </p>
            </div>
            <div class="cols-3">
                <img src="~/Image/StateImage/UttarPradesh/lucknow.jpg">
                <h3> Lucknow </h3>
                <p> The city is quite famous for its traditional chikan embroidery work, which attracts travellers from all across the country. The places to shop in Lucknow include the city's markets, with their narrow old lanes and countless shops, where shopping itself has its own charm.</p>
            </div>
